    public enum JdbcConnectionFactory
extends java.lang.Enum<JdbcConnectionFactory>
    Some JDBC Connections can be reused, for instance by a Dictionary and Concept Factory. This Singleton keeps a map of JDBC URLs to open and reusable Connections
